data.description: LAKEVIEW! Across the street from the community lake at Towamensing Trails, sits this modern 3 bedroom, 2 full bath cozy-chic mountain getaway. Enjoy the outdoors with THREE decks to take in the LAKE VIEWS and spacious yard w/ firepit. Bright and open concept GREAT ROOM w/ vaulted ceilings, stone fireplace, exposed beam, and fully stocked modern kitchen w/ granite. Bonus game room & loft areas add to the lounge spaces. Active Short-Term Vacation rental being sold Turn-Key & FULLY FURNISHED with bold & fun decor and chic modern furniture that stands out. Minutes from Jack Frost Big Boulder skiing, Hickory Run State Park & other mountain attractions. Walking distance to the community beach and amenities such as clubhouse, lake, outdoor pool, tennis court, and playground. This home has it all! Schedule to see it this week!
